OK. Found this, which SORTA answers my question that I asked you. But... Can we get a seed, please? I'll seed for a WHILE once it's done; whatta 'ya say, dias? Huh? In the wise and compelling words of one Peter Griffin, the great 'Socrates-like sage of our time, I got two words for ya: "C'MOOOONNN. Come oooooon. C'MOOOONNN"
Yep. How ya gonna argue with THAT!?
